<bibRefCitation author="DISTANT W. L." box="[374,490,654,673]" pageId="6" pageNumber="27" pagination="29 - 47" refId="ref13166" refString="DISTANT W. L. 1909: The Percy Sladen trust expedition to the Indian Ocean in 1905, under the leadership of Mr. J. Stanley Gardiner. Volume II. No. IV. &quot; Sealark &quot; Rhynchota. Transactions of the Linnean Society of London, Zoology 13 (1): 29 - 47 + 1 pl." type="journal article" year="1909">Distant, 1909</bibRefCitation>
